headline: 3 Red-Hot Dividend Stocks to Buy in May That Are Up Between 9% and 27% in 1 Month
summary: Deere is worth buying if you can endure its cyclicality.  Energy Transfer is a cash-gushing pipeline and infrastructure MLP with growth prospects under the Trump administration.  Huntington Ingalls is a defense contractor that reported a great start to 2025 and expects a strong performance for the rest of the year.
